## Step 2 — Create `apps/v4/registry/new-york-v4/examples/stepper-demo.tsx`

A 3-step horizontal stepper showing Account → Profile → Complete, with useState to manage `activeStep`, and Next/Previous navigation buttons. Uses `"use client"` (requires state). Follows the `default export function ComponentDemo()` pattern.

### Structure
